Manage custom analysis rules

Usage: normalize rules [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  add     Add a rule from a URL
  list    List installed rules
  update  Update imported rules from their sources
  remove  Remove an imported rule
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json       Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>  Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty     Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact    Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help       Print help
